author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Retail Estates Q3 Net Rental Income EUR 55.45‍​ Million, Up 13.79 Percent
text:
Feb 19 (Reuters) - RETAIL ESTATES NV:
* Q3 NET INCOME EUR 29.92‍​ MILLION * Q3 NET RENTAL INCOME EUR 55.45‍​ MILLION, UP 13.79 PERCENT
* OCCUPANCY RATE AT END-DEC. 98.31‍​ PERCENT VERSUS 98.13% AT END-MARCH
* Q3 EPRA RESULT EUR 33.91 MILLION VERSUS EUR 28.05 MILLION YEAR AGO
* END-DEC. FAIR VALUE OF REAL ESTATE PORTFOLIO EUR 1.33 BILLION
* EXPECTED DIVIDEND INCREASED TO EUR 3.60 GROSS PER SHARE * MACROECONOMIC UNCERTAINTIES DON‘T ALLOW PREDICTIONS ABOUT CHANGES IN FAIR VALUE OF INTEREST RATE HEDGING INSTRUMENTS
* MACROECONOMIC UNCERTAINTIES DON‘T ALLOW PREDICTIONS ABOUT EVOLUTION OF FAIR VALUE OF INVESTMENT PROPERTIES Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
